casebody.data:
Kenneth D. BOBBITT
v.
David MITCHELL, Roy Cooper. No. 645P03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2004. Kenneth D. Bobbitt, Pro Se. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, for Mitchell, Cooper.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 10th day of December 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2004."
